snippet.title: Castlevania Blood Moon
snippet.description: One of the most extensive Castlevania hacks out there, Blood Moon features new enemies, graphics, and all new level design. Other changes include the ability to whip while walking! A fantastic fan made game that is sure to please any Castlevania fan!
